<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>お部屋情報登録</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <style>
      /* Always set the map height explicitly to define the size of the div
       * element that contains the map. */
      #map {
        height: 450px;
        width: 484px;
      }
      /* Optional: Makes the sample page fill the window. */
      html, body {
        height: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
    </style>
    <style type="text/css">
    a:link { color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="main-content">
      <div class="new-header">
        <button type="button" class="button-style">airbnb</button>
        <div class="comp-left">
          <span class="h5 text-normal">ステップ１：最初は基本情報から</span>
        </div>
        <div class="comp-right">
          <a>保存して閉じる</a>
        </div>
        <div class="progress" style="height:5px;">
        <div class="progress-bar bg-info" role="progressbar" style="width: 80%" aria-valuenow="80" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="left-content">
        <div class="left-content-list">
          <div class="rooms-title">
            <span class="rooms-title-font">所在地は？</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rooms-location-space">
            <h5>入力された住所がリンク</h5>
            <%= link_to '住所を編集する', new_room_location_path, class: "rooms-adress-edit" %>
          </div>

          <div id="map"></div>
          <script>
            var map;
            function initMap() {
              map = new google.maps.Map(document.getElementById('map'), {
                center: {lat: gon.latitude, lng: gon.longitude},
                zoom: 12
              });
            }
          </script>
          <script src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyBni7w26AcUziUF-q9RO0NxsvB9OldANiQ&callback=initMap"
          async defer></script>

          <div class="rooms-location-comment">ピンをドラッグすると場所を変更できます。</div>

          <div class="main-panel-action-wrapper">
            <div class="main-panel-half-content clearfix">
              <div class="main-panel-half-spacce">
                <div class="main-panel-half">
                  <%= link_to '← 戻る', new_room_location_path, class: 'h5 rooms-back-font' %>
                  <%= link_to '次へ', new_room_amenity_path, class: 'rooms-next-btn' %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="helper-content">
        <div class="helper-content-list">
          <div class="card card-style rounded-0" style="width: 20rem;">
            <img class="card-img-top">
            <div class="card-body">
              <span class="fa fa-lightbulb-o fa-3x text-info" aria-hidden="true"></span><br>
              <p class="card-text text-muted">具体的な住所は、予約確定後までゲストにも秘密です。</p><br>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
